<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>E-Shop API Documentation</title>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
        <style>
            .code-editor {
                background-color: #2d2d2d;
                color: #f8f8f2;
                padding: 10px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                overflow-x: auto;
                font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
        <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">E-Shop API Documentation</h1>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Generate API Key</h2>
                <p>To use the API, you need to generate an API key. No sign-up is required.</p>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>POST /generate-api-key</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Example Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>
fetch("https://react-e-shop-silk.vercel.app/generate-api-key", {
    method: "POST"
})
.then(response => response.json())
.then(data => console.log(data))
.catch(error => console.error("Error:", error));
        </code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Example Response</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>
{
    "apiKey": "exampleb7dd5afd3a0b557c904fc2ecc3ayy234d8b3e660bab1a736030d8b54"
}
        </code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Get Products</h2>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>GET /products?currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Query Parameters</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>currentPage:</strong> number (The page you want, default = 1)</li>
                    <li><strong>itemPerPage:</strong> number (Number of products per page, default = 10)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Example Response</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>
{
    "products": [
        {
            "id": 232,
            "name": "Wireless Headphones",
            "price": 99.99,
            "description": "High-quality wireless headphones with noise-cancellation and long battery life.",
            "type": "electronics",
            "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/wireless-headphones.jpg"
        },
        {
            "id": 233,
            "name": "Bluetooth Speaker",
            "price": 49.99,
            "description": "Portable Bluetooth speaker with excellent sound quality and battery life.",
            "type": "electronics",
            "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/bluetooth-speaker.jpg"
        },
        {
            "id": 234,
            "name": "Smartwatch",
            "price": 199.99,
            "description": "Feature-packed smartwatch with fitness tracking, heart rate monitoring, and notifications.",
            "type": "electronics",
            "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/smartwatch.jpg"
        }
        ...
    ]
}
        </code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Search Products</h2>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Search by Description</h3>
                <pre
                    class="code-editor mb-4"><code>GET /products/search/description?description=value&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Query Parameters</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>description:</strong> string (Keyword for searching)</li>
                    <li><strong>currentPage:</strong> number</li>
                    <li><strong>itemPerPage:</strong> number</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Example Response</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>
                {
                    "products": [
                        {
                            "id": 234,
                            "name": "Smartwatch",
                            "price": 199.99,
                            "description": "Feature-packed smartwatch with fitness tracking, heart rate monitoring, and notifications.",
                            "type": "electronics",
                            "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/smartwatch.jpg"
                        }
                        ...
                    ]
                }
        </code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Search by Other Fields</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><code>GET /products/search/type?type=value&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></li>
                    <li><code>GET /products/search/name?name=value&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></li>
                    <li><code>GET /products/search/price?price=value&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></li>
                    <li>
                        <code
                            >GET
                            /products/search/eqPrice?minPrice=value1&maxPrice=value2&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li><code>GET /products/search/id?id=value&currentPage=2&itemPerPage=20</code></li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Query Parameters</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>type, name:</strong> string (Filter for product type)</li>
                    <li><strong>minPrice, maxPrice, price:</strong> number</li>
                    <li><strong>currentPage:</strong> number</li>
                    <li><strong>itemPerPage:</strong> number</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Get Product Details</h2>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>GET /product-details/:id</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Path Parameter</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>id:</strong> number (The ID of the product)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Example Response</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>
[{
    "id": 235,
    "name": "4K Ultra HD Smart TV",
    "price": 499.99,
    "description": "Experience stunning visuals with this 55-inch 4K Ultra HD Smart TV, featuring HDR support and voice control.",
    "type": "electronics",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/4k-smart-tv.jpg",
    "stock": 50,
    "ratings": 4.7
}]
        </code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Post Product</h2>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>POST /post-product</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Required Parameters</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>name:</strong> product's name (type: string)</li>
                    <li><strong>price:</strong> (type: number)</li>
                    <li><strong>description:</strong> about product (type: string)</li>
                    <li><strong>type:</strong> (type: string)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Rate Products</h2>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Request</h3>
                <pre class="code-editor mb-4"><code>POST /rating</code></pre>

                <h3 class="font-semibold">Required Parameters</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li><strong>id:</strong> product's id (type: string)</li>
                    <li><strong>userId:</strong> (type: string)</li>
                    <li><strong>rating:</strong> (type: number), max value 5</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
